        public StringValue(Grammar.Token token,

                   Trackable trackable)
        Create a string token value.
        Parameters:
        token - The token in the grammar that produced that value.
        value - The actual value.
        trackable - The scanner from which the value was read. If the scanner is a trackable scanner, informations about the position of the value will be available.

      • StringValue

        Create a string token value.
        Parameters:
        token - The token in the grammar that produced that value.
        value - The actual value as a Unicode codepoint.
        trackable - The scanner from which the value was read. If the scanner is a trackable scanner, informations about the position of the value will be available.
